<codeline><highlight class="normal">#<sp/>Kokkos:<sp/>Core<sp/>Libraries</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">Kokkos<sp/>Core<sp/>implements<sp/>a<sp/>programming<sp/>model<sp/>in<sp/>C++<sp/>for<sp/>writing<sp/>performance<sp/>portable</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">applications<sp/>targeting<sp/>all<sp/>major<sp/>HPC<sp/>platforms.<sp/>For<sp/>that<sp/>purpose<sp/>it<sp/>provides</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">abstractions<sp/>for<sp/>both<sp/>parallel<sp/>execution<sp/>of<sp/>code<sp/>and<sp/>data<sp/>management.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">Kokkos<sp/>is<sp/>designed<sp/>to<sp/>target<sp/>complex<sp/>node<sp/>architectures<sp/>with<sp/>N-level<sp/>memory</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">hierarchies<sp/>and<sp/>multiple<sp/>types<sp/>of<sp/>execution<sp/>resources.<sp/>It<sp/>currently<sp/>can<sp/>use</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">CUDA,<sp/>HIP,<sp/>SYCL,<sp/>HPX,<sp/>OpenMP<sp/>and<sp/>C++<sp/>threads<sp/>as<sp/>backend<sp/>programming<sp/>models<sp/>with<sp/>several<sp/>other</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">backends<sp/>in<sp/>development.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">Kokkos<sp/>Core<sp/>is<sp/>part<sp/>of<sp/>the<sp/>Kokkos<sp/>C++<sp/>Performance<sp/>Portability<sp/>Programming<sp/>EcoSystem,</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">which<sp/>also<sp/>provides<sp/>math<sp/>kernels<sp/>(https://github.com/kokkos/kokkos-kernels),<sp/>as<sp/>well<sp/>as</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">profiling<sp/>and<sp/>debugging<sp/>tools<sp/>(https://github.com/kokkos/kokkos-tools).</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">#<sp/>Learning<sp/>about<sp/>Kokkos</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">The<sp/>best<sp/>way<sp/>to<sp/>start<sp/>learning<sp/>about<sp/>Kokkos<sp/>is<sp/>going<sp/>through<sp/>the<sp/>Kokkos<sp/>Lectures.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">They<sp/>are<sp/>online<sp/>available<sp/>at<sp/>https://kokkos.link/the-lectures<sp/>and<sp/>contain<sp/>a<sp/>mix</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">of<sp/>lecture<sp/>videos<sp/>and<sp/>hands-on<sp/>exercises<sp/>covering<sp/>all<sp/>the<sp/>important<sp/>Kokkos<sp/>Ecosystem</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">capabilities.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">A<sp/>programming<sp/>guide<sp/>and<sp/>API<sp/>reference<sp/>can<sp/>be<sp/>found<sp/>on<sp/>the<sp/>Wiki</highlight></codeline>
