<codeline><highlight class="normal">with<sp/>warnings<sp/>as<sp/>errors.<sp/>They<sp/>also<sp/>are<sp/>tested<sp/>with<sp/>a<sp/>comprehensive<sp/>set<sp/>of</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">backend<sp/>combinations<sp/>(i.e.<sp/>OpenMP,<sp/>Pthreads,<sp/>Serial,<sp/>OpenMP+Serial,<sp/>...).</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">We<sp/>are<sp/>using<sp/>the<sp/>following<sp/>set<sp/>of<sp/>flags:</highlight></codeline>
