<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>-Wall<sp/>-Wunused-parameter<sp/>-Wshadow<sp/>-pedantic</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>-Werror<sp/>-Wsign-compare<sp/>-Wtype-limits</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>-Wuninitialized</highlight></codeline>
